<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Quiz · 2-letter words · Scrabble Words Finder</p>


      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>7 min read</span>
